{"tid":474374,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"迪士尼掹Pluto鬍鬚 被勸阻竟毆傷員工","createTime":"2017-11-20T06:10:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-20T06:10:18.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"4c17e5d1392732885ae5440c0b3a0bffc717e1ea","tid":474374,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T06:10:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171120/large/1511152504_5e66.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171120%2Flarge%2F1511152504_5e66.jpg&h=f8c13863&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n強國打人事件頻生，最新一宗是網爆上海迪士尼有人拉「布魯托（Pluto）」鬍鬚，被勸阻後毆打樂園攝影師。<br />\n<br />\n前日有網友爆料指，上海迪士尼裡有人毆打工作人員，原因竟然是肇事者被樂園攝影師提醒，不要拉布魯托的鬍鬚，根據網友描述，肇事的一男一女不僅理虧還態度蠻橫，「女的破口大罵，男的直接對樂園攝影師打了上去，還說：「把你打瞎又怎麼樣！」這件事情被曝光後，網友紛紛大駡這對男女「沒素質」，「這男的全家老少終生禁止再入迪士尼樂園，全球任何樂園都禁止入內。就該這麼治這些沒素質的」；「這種人罰了鞭刑！不打記不住的貨色！」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20171120/57480868\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171120%2F57480868&d=s5%2BDHZkeGHiw0ctAYStYKwHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=c5172cf3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171120%2F57480868&h=a0dbadbf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20171120/57480868</a>"}]}